   438                        ;
   439                        ;This routine tests that the IDE Controller is ready and can accept a command for execution.
   440                        ; There are two bits in the status register to qualify this:
   441                        ; Bit 6 is for Ready and bit 4 is for Seek Complete. Both should be active to qualify the
